w\left(\cfrac Q {1+\frac w r}\right)^2 + r\left(\cfrac Q {1 + \frac r w}\right)^2
\cfrac {Q^2} {\frac 1 w + \frac 1 r}
\displaystyle\frac a{\left(\dfrac bc\right)}=\frac{ac}b,
\displaystyle\frac {\left(\dfrac ab\right)}c=\frac a{bc}
\frac Q{1+\dfrac wr}=\frac Q{\dfrac{r+w}r}=\frac{Qr}{r+w}
\implies w\left(\frac Q{1+\dfrac wr}\right)^2=\frac{Q^2r^2w}{(r+w)^2}
r\left(\frac Q{1+\dfrac rw}\right)^2=\frac{Q^2rw^2}{(r+w)^2}
\frac{Q^2rw^2+Q^2r^2w}{(r+w)^2}=\frac{Q^2rw(r+w)}{(r+w)^2}=\frac{Q^2rw}{(r+w)}
rw
rw(r+w)\ne0
